node.text: @foodie_kitchn try it :) lots of tutorials on YouTube

Been wanting to try wrapping my own sandwich 😃..I did it :) this mega sandwich with things in my fridge and am I stuffed after just eating 1/2 of it with my coffee 😋🤣 the other half became my tea break 😛
.
Swipe to see what I have added in :)
Eat well , rest well everyone !
@fatwithin thanks Christina 😀 taste great too but too much for me 🤣
@cassakating taste great too 🤣 aiyo how can self praise de 😂
@cforcoffeee act smart la me .. add so much things 😂
@crappysotong too ambitious .. added too much things
@sgfoodfinder hahah wanted the flavours are so good combined but yeah too much 😂
Wa teach me hw to wrap lei hahaha
@aprilyap 😂made during week day while he was at work .. one half for lunch and the other I had it for tea time 🤓😋
Huge sandwich! Share with your hubby, 一人一半，感情不散💕
@hearwhiff cannot 😂 tried to compress it before I bite 😹
haha so big! looks good but the mouth can fit? 😂
